spec_data.Name: jackson-dataformat-csv
spec_data.Description:
Jackson data format module for reading and writing CSV encoded data,
either as "raw" data (sequence of String arrays), or via data binding to
from Java Objects (POJOs).
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 06:12:40 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Jackson extension for adding support for reading and writing CSV formatted data
